        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare genetic primary bone dysplasia disorder characterized by disproportionate short stature with mesomelic short limbs leg bowing lumbar lordosis brachydactyly joint laxity and a waddling gait. Radiographs show platyspondyly with central protrusion of anterior vertebral bodies kyphotic angulation and very short long bones with dysplastic epiphyses and flarred irregular cupped metaphyses."
        },
